Modifications
-------------
Mantishack ships the RAPTOR source tree with a repository-wide rebrand
(raptor -> mantishack / mantis across file names, identifiers, and prose),
the slash commands renamed to the /mantis-* namespace, a new authentication
and security-logging Semgrep audit lane (engine/semgrep/rules/auth/*.yaml,
engine/semgrep/rules/logging/missing-auth-audit.yaml, plus the pytest
auth_audit fixtures), and a mascot asset (docs/assets/mascot/hero.png).

The upstream LICENSE and CITATION.cff are preserved byte-for-byte and still
credit the RAPTOR authors. Other files — including CLAUDE.md, agent prompts,
skills, and source modules — were modified by the rebrand and are NOT
preserved unmodified relative to the upstream commit. Attribution to RAPTOR
is retained through this NOTICE, the LICENSE file, CITATION.cff, and the
top-level README, which identifies this repository as a fork.
